      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks. those are good starting points, but they're a bit broad. can you go deeper on the 'rule of law' aspect? specifically, how would someone argue that failing to strictly enforce the border actually undermines the legal integrity of the entire immigration system? i want them to have a really sophisticated philosophical angle for it.",
